text:
Tonight is our developer meetup at Democracy Brewing! Come and join your fellow devs and the HubSpotters that love you from 6-10 PM for free beer, seltzers, mocktails and tasty tasty food for everyone - and some wacky surprises :slightly_smiling_face:  I wish I could share our RSVP list - ALL THE COOL KIDS WILL BE THERE!

We still have room, so if you want to nab a ticket, <https://events.HubSpot.com/events/details/HubSpot-HubSpot-global-presents-developers-inbound-meetup/?code=devslackog|here you go>!
Don't forget to come see is at HubSpot HQ's demo station - if you ask someone at the <Developer + Ecosystem> station nicely enough, you may walk home with a lovely little surprise!

In 15 minutes, <@U05Q7VCN92S> Seligson and <@UD53A9UUR> will take the HubSpot Heroes stage and show you how to leverage the HubSpot platform to supercharge your business. You're not going to want to miss this one! Mosey on down to HubSpot HQ, won't ya?
